	<clause id="_feature_relationship" obligation="normative"><title>Feature Relationship</title><p id="_753bbb46-1731-4cfa-b234-b9c850327551">A feature relationship links instances of one feature type with instances of the same or a different feature type. There are three common types of feature relationship: Association, Aggregation and Composition.</p>
	<p id="_be70d24e-7bf9-4ace-8131-625dcb1838b7">S-102 uses only one type of feature relationship: Association.</p>
